OL,3,C'Truly broken' Family business
OL,4,Ctargeted twice by thieves loses #30k
OL,5,Cin takings
OL,7,FThe owner of a convenience store in
OL,8,FOxfordshire says the emotional impact
OL,9,Fof being burgled twice in three months
OL,10,Fhas been devastating for his family.
OL,12,FThe SPAR in Minster Lovell, near
OL,13,FWitney, was first targeted in
OL,14,FSeptember 2024.
OL,16,FFour masked assailants forced their
OL,17,Fway in but took nothing, leaving
OL,18,Fbehind broken shutters and doors.
