OL,7,FThe day after Boxing Day, thieves
OL,8,Freturned and ram raided the newly
OL,9,Ffixed door. They made off with the
OL,10,Fcash machine, which had about #2,500
OL,11,Finside.
OL,13,FAround #1,000 in stock was lost, there
OL,14,Fwas damage to fridges and doors and
OL,15,Fbroken glass everywhere.
