OL,7,FAs the shop reopened, they had to
OL,8,Fboard up the doors. This has meant
OL,9,Fpassing trade has significantly
OL,10,Fdecreased, leaving Ian Lewis, the
OL,11,Fowner, about #30,000 down - like for
OL,12,Flike on the year before.
OL,14,F"You're looking at the account every
OL,15,Fsingle day," said Mr Lewis.
OL,17,F"With direct debits still going out,
OL,18,Fpeople still need paying, staff still
OL,19,Fneed to be paid.
