OL,7,F"But unfortunately, the footfall
OL,8,Fbecause of the boards, it looks like
OL,9,Fwe are closed."
OL,11,FThe business has been in Mr Lewis's
OL,12,Ffamily for generations, set up by his
OL,13,Fgrandmother in 1937.
OL,15,FHis parents live next door and have
OL,16,Fbeen significantly affected by the
OL,17,Fbreak-ins.
OL,19,FThey were sleeping upstairs during
OL,20,Fboth incidents.
