OL,7,FHis father, David, felt hopeless as
OL,8,Fthere were five men outside: "When
OL,9,Fthey'd gone, we opened the door into
OL,10,Fthe shop and just saw the devastation,
OL,11,Fwe both burst into tears."
OL,13,FMr Lewis feels as if he's "grieving
OL,14,Fhis parents" and his mother is "truly
OL,15,Fbroken", saying they have changed so
OL,16,Fmuch since the latest incident.
