OL,7,FMr Lewis has considered giving up the
OL,8,Fbusiness, in the immediate aftermath
OL,9,Fof the Christmas burglary, but said
OL,10,Fall the support during the "dark week"
OL,11,Fhas motivated him to keep going.
OL,13,FA customer set up a fundraising page
OL,14,Ffor new shutters, which has raised
OL,15,Fmore than #2,500 in cash. Described as
OL,16,Fthe "cornerstone of the village", he
OL,17,Fsaid all the support for the business
OL,18,Fhas been "really heartwarming".
